fulltitle: Martin Taylor - advice for guitar players -talks to Keith Nolan
description: I met with one of the most amazing jazz guitar masters in the world Martin Taylor and apart from having played on over 100 albums and been one of the worlds greatest, Martin is one of the most humble and down to earth people I have ever met. We talk about his recent album with Tommy Emanuel "The Colonel and the Governor" a truly amazing pure even organic album, I highly recommend it ! Martin shared his thoughts on music, touring working with Tommy Emanuel , about his guitar and love for music and his advice for young guitar players getting into the music biz ! I was honored to interview him in Bangkok at his album launch on Keith Nolan's Access All Areas. Big thanks to Martin !
